                                Want to develop awesome web apps? Get started with ASP NET Core
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/banner2.svg" alt="Visual Studio" class="img-responsive" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                        <p>
                            <a class="btn btn-link white-links" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=525030&clcid=0x409">
                                Love complete and usefull tools? Download Visual Studio
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/banner3.svg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
